{"tid":308194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華盛頓火車出軌翻覆 267乘客僅數人輕傷","createTime":"2017-07-04T03:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T08:48:59.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f99684eefc4990dc0fe6b235d1b568507e0307c3","tid":308194,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:17:59.000Z","msg":"華盛頓火車出軌翻覆 267乘客僅數人輕傷<br />\n<br />\n2017-07-04 10:05<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國華盛頓州1列火車在7月2日下午2時30分，於錢伯斯灣大橋（Chambers Bay Bridge）出軌，車上共載有267名乘客，只有數人受到輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，當地消防局指出，該列火車共有15節車廂，前4節車廂發生脫軌，橫躺在鐵軌旁。美國國家鐵路客運公司指出，事故中沒有重大傷亡，所有乘客都被疏散，以其他交通工具接駁離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2120329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2120329&d=SkA8WLdlFgKU%2BE%2FaJD6IKMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ece39da0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2120329&h=5e8c4f1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2120329</a>"},{"pid":"1bc5a965bfc1a8e854172c85d1aa07a58ef80056","tid":308194,"uid":5462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:20:18.000Z","msg":"如果發生係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d6086f39ca0651d0a98792e143c8d4f5547cea","tid":308194,"uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果發生係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n也不超過37"},{"pid":"030a213b9acdc37fbafbcf05c1b00ccb6f7f2c47","tid":308194,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"美國啲火車，技術係舊啲，車速係慢啲，但起碼扎扎實實畀足料<br />\n至於強國......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab27bb5fc1a3610ec9341a8b387de8c25c94e991","tid":308194,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"rep